body_html:
Can you use the latest version of TensorFlow and build by any chance?

Unfortunately, when I try to build release 1.11 I get 48 errors of the type C1083. Specifically tf_core_lib.vcxproj complains that stringpiece.h cannot find a file, namely ""absl/strings/string_view.h": No such file or directory".

Cheers!
